        <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Given its separating abilities, the decanter finds a variety of applications in biotechnology separation, oil fields, <a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">wastewater treatment</a>, the food industry, and many other industrial processes.</p>
